It also contains new support cards for Fairy monsters (such as the "Majestic Mechs"), and support for Cyber Girls, the "Elemental HERO" archetype, Machines and WIND monsters. Highly sought after cards include "Macro Cosmos", "Cyber Phoenix", "Voltanis the Adjudicator" and "Majestic Mech - Ohka".
